%% 依据：src/index.ts、src/stdin.ts、src/transcript.ts、src/render/index.ts；真实 stdin payload 待采样验证。
sequenceDiagram
  participant CC as Claude Code
  participant Cmd as statusLine.command
  participant Main as src/index.ts
  participant Transcript as src/transcript.ts
  participant Render as src/render

  CC->>Cmd: invoke with stdin JSON
  Cmd->>Main: run dist/index.js
  Main->>Main: readStdin()
  Main->>Transcript: parseTranscript(transcript_path)
  Transcript-->>Main: tools, agents, todos, session tokens
  Main->>Main: load config, git, usage, memory, version
  Main->>Render: render(RenderContext)
  Render-->>CC: stdout HUD lines
